seeded and cut into strips","140 g fresh green beans, trimmed and cut into halves","400 g canned kidney beans, rinsed and drained (approx. 250 g after draining)","300 g vine-ripened tomatoes, cut into eighths","salt, to taste (optional)","100 g Greek-style natural yoghurt","fresh coriander leaves, to serve"]}],"id":"r150465","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-0bJsjsQcHkU\/XZVQ8l_28qI\/AAAAAAAAdHs\/6ovHu-t7-js_3pzbfcXv9vjeR63qdc9EgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_anDu6ZRVrcCawvIt.png","title":"Caribbean curry","publishedAt":"2018-04-02T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"8.2 g","fat":"16.2 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"17 g","calories":"1100 kJ \/ 262 kcal"},"usefulItems":"sealable container, thermal serving bowl or other large bowl","hintsAndTricks":["You can store the Caribbean spice mix in a sealable container in the pantry for up to 3 months.","Please refer to <i>The Basic Cookbook<\/i> or <i>Everyday Cookbook<\/i> for the Vegetable stock paste recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","40m","6 portions"]}